column54: Want to keep my kids in the same school
Want to keep my kids in the same school

My daughter Eden would like to stay in her school since she has established relationships with students and staff. I dont think it would be beneficial for her to uproot her to her 3rd NHPS. I am hopeful that her little sister, Kori will be accepted to Davis so that they can be in the same school together. It has been incredibly difficult with them being in two separate schools all year.
